      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LONE HUNTER (1) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 3.5 lengths (23.90) at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Can make amends. AKELA KUNG FU (2) failed to feature last start after missing the jump at this track, but prior to that won by 0.8 lengths at this track (30.15) beating Wilma Flintstone in a Grade 5/6 on May 10. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. DAYSEA'S ELVIS (7) had been in super honest form hitting the frame four times on end before finishing fifth (24.45) at this track last time. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from eight starts. Can figure in the finish. FARMOR ROGUE (6) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.",
